faceoff_negative.comments:
Love the color (685 Midnight Kiss) and formulation. Rich color, long-lasting, softening, comfortable. 

However, the case feels very lightweight and cheap compared to the previous lipstick line (Pure Color Envy) that this appears to have replaced. The previous lipstick cases had a high-quality, heavy weight to them and were almost like collectible keepsakes. This case feels like a drugstore lipstick that would be less than half the price. Recently with inflation, I've noticed not only prices of  all types of products increasing, but also quality plummeting. 

@Estée Lauder - you have been one of the most reliable beauty brands for a long time. Please don't follow this trend of companies cutting corners on quality, charging the same (or higher) prices, trying to pass something off as the same product (when it's not), and hoping customers won't notice (we do!). You may cut costs in the short term, but you will lose formerly loyal customers in the long run. I want to be able to trust this brand.
